{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-index-js","path":"/matrix-robotics/","result":{"data":{"site":{"meta":{"title":"Ansin","description":"Ansin's portfolio","url":"https://imyentsen.github.io","author":"Ansinlau","twitter":"Ansinlau","adsense":""}},"post":{"id":"79e674da-666b-5440-aeca-ffe08a0b42fe","html":"<p>MATRIX Robotics would like to renovate its official website and upgrade it to a newer version of WordPress CMS. I developed an agile roadmap with them to redefine the website structure and to create a novel website UI system. The UI design complies with both the new componentized WordPress Gutenberg block system and the established branding style of MATRIX Robotics.</p>\n<h3>Agile roadmap for design development</h3>\n<p>The project lasted around 2 months with four agile cycles. Throughout the iterations, there were four core members involved: a project manager, a full-stack engineer, a branding designer, and I. The iterations allowed us to develop the new website UI system from a rough and general level of scale to every top-notch detail.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Agile roadmap\" title src=\"/static/bd2faf194931e057c03ff26bf04411ca/3acf0/slide-1.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/bd2faf194931e057c03ff26bf04411ca/41099/slide-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/bd2faf194931e057c03ff26bf04411ca/a2510/slide-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/bd2faf194931e057c03ff26bf04411ca/3acf0/slide-1.jpg 2000w,\n/static/bd2faf194931e057c03ff26bf04411ca/a35ba/slide-1.jpg 2161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>The roadmap of the project</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>Each cycle took two weeks. At the end of each cycle, we arranged a meeting for progress reporting, feedback gathering, and evaluation. The meetings were the key events where the team members brainstormed and gathered the ideas for further design improvements.</p>\n<p>In the first cycle, we collaboratively refined the requirements of the project, which included the website structure, and module functions. It was our first-time collaboration and the client company did not have any previous experience working with external design professionals in website design. As such, I introduced the concepts of agile cycles and design iterations to them and concretized the timeframe and schedule of the project. It took two rounds of meetings between the executive teams, and several other internal meetings for the communication across the company departments. Finally, we established a nested list of website structure. Every item on the list was agreed upon based on continuous communication during this cycle.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 1698px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 63.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Part of the website structure\" title src=\"/static/f3c59340b439ef8e7aa4609b7036c62f/5c489/webStructure.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/f3c59340b439ef8e7aa4609b7036c62f/41099/webStructure.jpg 500w,\n/static/f3c59340b439ef8e7aa4609b7036c62f/a2510/webStructure.jpg 1000w,\n/static/f3c59340b439ef8e7aa4609b7036c62f/5c489/webStructure.jpg 1698w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1698px) 100vw, 1698px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Part of the website structure</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>In the second cycle, I developed the wireframes of the pages and the WordPress modules inside each page. With the wireframes, I built up a mockup of rather low-fidelity. The mockup helped us to focus on the functionalities and arrangement of the webpages. We checked if every item on the list have been fulfilled, and we also discussed if there is any better way on the wireframe level to achieve the same functionalities.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 62.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Part of the website wireframe\" title src=\"/static/9f6af2649a504b9813b505730d2800a8/3acf0/wireframe.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/9f6af2649a504b9813b505730d2800a8/41099/wireframe.jpg 500w,\n/static/9f6af2649a504b9813b505730d2800a8/a2510/wireframe.jpg 1000w,\n/static/9f6af2649a504b9813b505730d2800a8/3acf0/wireframe.jpg 2000w,\n/static/9f6af2649a504b9813b505730d2800a8/1db01/wireframe.jpg 2744w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Part of the website wireframe</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>In the third cycle, I kept improving the wireframes based on the feedback agreed in the previous meeting. I also created the general guidelines for the website visual style. We arranged a meeting to review the results on both sides. Throughout the cycle, I also worked closely with the engineer to ensure that the file structure on Figma is comprehensive for further handoff.</p>\n<p>In the last round, I applied the general guidelines of website visual style to the wireframes. As we have concretized the overall wireframes of the site, the effort on the style application won’t be made in vain due to unexpected changes. At the end of the cycle, I completed an exhaustive design system with abundant details. The meeting of this round was a final review of all the outcome. We also arranged several other meetups for the complete handoff to the engineering team of the company.</p>\n<h3>Website UI system</h3>\n<p>Based on the overall website and module structure, we built up a scaffolding where the UI guidelines and the further design implementation situated. The UI guidelines are a system that describes the overall logic of the website interaction､ such as the mental model that determines the general layout arrangement and the events regarding mouse and finger movements.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"A glance at the threefold web UI system\" title src=\"/static/9eec3071bfa8167c1dca094e59558d8b/3acf0/slide-2.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/9eec3071bfa8167c1dca094e59558d8b/41099/slide-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/9eec3071bfa8167c1dca094e59558d8b/a2510/slide-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/9eec3071bfa8167c1dca094e59558d8b/3acf0/slide-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/9eec3071bfa8167c1dca094e59558d8b/a35ba/slide-2.jpg 2161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>A glance at the threefold web UI system</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>The logic of the UI system is the “why” of the user interface. The interactions and their elements are the “how” to achieve the “why”. We asked about how the users would do to experience consistent interactions, for example, how would the users know that a section is more important than the others? How could we design the section and its visual language to facilitate them with a higher priority in interaction?</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Brightness and satuation in the visual priority of page components\" title src=\"/static/d37c195a2022481dca6905b78cb3bbea/3acf0/slide-3.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/d37c195a2022481dca6905b78cb3bbea/41099/slide-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/d37c195a2022481dca6905b78cb3bbea/a2510/slide-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/d37c195a2022481dca6905b78cb3bbea/3acf0/slide-3.jpg 2000w,\n/static/d37c195a2022481dca6905b78cb3bbea/a35ba/slide-3.jpg 2161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Brightness and saturation, two of the determining factors of the UI logic, in the visual priority of page components.</figcaption>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"A metaphore of shadow\" title src=\"/static/5e2147837814d1ffa0fa6cf6b3187e52/3acf0/slide-4.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/5e2147837814d1ffa0fa6cf6b3187e52/41099/slide-4.jpg 500w,\n/static/5e2147837814d1ffa0fa6cf6b3187e52/a2510/slide-4.jpg 1000w,\n/static/5e2147837814d1ffa0fa6cf6b3187e52/3acf0/slide-4.jpg 2000w,\n/static/5e2147837814d1ffa0fa6cf6b3187e52/274e1/slide-4.jpg 2160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>A metaphor of shadow helps to build up the mental model of the mouse/finger movements.</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p>At the bottom of the system is the most “grounded” part of the whole system, such as the color palette and the typographic system. For the interactable components on the webpage, there are also a few default settings in common, such as the transition animation of the fading process.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"The color palette of the web UI system\" title src=\"/static/5aaa80e31cf343cea75437076cafcffb/3acf0/slide-5.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/5aaa80e31cf343cea75437076cafcffb/41099/slide-5.jpg 500w,\n/static/5aaa80e31cf343cea75437076cafcffb/a2510/slide-5.jpg 1000w,\n/static/5aaa80e31cf343cea75437076cafcffb/3acf0/slide-5.jpg 2000w,\n/static/5aaa80e31cf343cea75437076cafcffb/a35ba/slide-5.jpg 2161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>The color palette of the web UI system. It also complies with the established branding style of the client company.</figcaption>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Responsive typographics of the web UI system\" title src=\"/static/6f136491d5856020225472dfc4a1a69a/3acf0/slide-6.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/6f136491d5856020225472dfc4a1a69a/41099/slide-6.jpg 500w,\n/static/6f136491d5856020225472dfc4a1a69a/a2510/slide-6.jpg 1000w,\n/static/6f136491d5856020225472dfc4a1a69a/3acf0/slide-6.jpg 2000w,\n/static/6f136491d5856020225472dfc4a1a69a/274e1/slide-6.jpg 2160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Responsive typographic of the web UI system: the fonts shown on tablets are a little larger than the other two size ranges (desktop and mobile).</figcaption>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Metaphore of shadow for the interactions triggered by the mouse/finger movements\" title src=\"/static/09f3f2db2e3980c01d5c77666b9ebb77/3acf0/slide-7.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/09f3f2db2e3980c01d5c77666b9ebb77/41099/slide-7.jpg 500w,\n/static/09f3f2db2e3980c01d5c77666b9ebb77/a2510/slide-7.jpg 1000w,\n/static/09f3f2db2e3980c01d5c77666b9ebb77/3acf0/slide-7.jpg 2000w,\n/static/09f3f2db2e3980c01d5c77666b9ebb77/a35ba/slide-7.jpg 2161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>The icon set: the icons look consistent, and the mouse/finger interaction also follows the same mental model of shadow and brightness.</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<h3>Implementation of design</h3>\n<p>Applying the guidelines to the wireframe is the last step of the design process. In the meantime during this final stage, I was also working closely with the engineers of the company in order to make the coming handoff go more smoothly.</p>\n<p>I typically share part of the working files with the engineers a few weeks earlier than the actual handoff so that we could check how to properly export and interpret the design into codes together. In this project, we used the working files to build a minor part of the landing page as a “pilot run”. It also helped me to find several interactions missing in my design.</p>\n<hr>\n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Implementation of design\" title src=\"/static/5ae7009c5f606131d553ea5b1b89f4a7/3acf0/slide-8.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/5ae7009c5f606131d553ea5b1b89f4a7/41099/slide-8.jpg 500w,\n/static/5ae7009c5f606131d553ea5b1b89f4a7/a2510/slide-8.jpg 1000w,\n/static/5ae7009c5f606131d553ea5b1b89f4a7/3acf0/slide-8.jpg 2000w,\n/static/5ae7009c5f606131d553ea5b1b89f4a7/a35ba/slide-8.jpg 2161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Implementation of design\" title src=\"/static/78de28881229eca7282de55b81bf9dca/3acf0/slide-9.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/78de28881229eca7282de55b81bf9dca/41099/slide-9.jpg 500w,\n/static/78de28881229eca7282de55b81bf9dca/a2510/slide-9.jpg 1000w,\n/static/78de28881229eca7282de55b81bf9dca/3acf0/slide-9.jpg 2000w,\n/static/78de28881229eca7282de55b81bf9dca/274e1/slide-9.jpg 2160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem; max-width: 2000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 71.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Implementation of design\" title src=\"/static/c754edd8b7be82e123a31da198a4ca54/3acf0/slide-10.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/c754edd8b7be82e123a31da198a4ca54/41099/slide-10.jpg 500w,\n/static/c754edd8b7be82e123a31da198a4ca54/a2510/slide-10.jpg 1000w,\n/static/c754edd8b7be82e123a31da198a4ca54/3acf0/slide-10.jpg 2000w,\n/static/c754edd8b7be82e123a31da198a4ca54/a35ba/slide-10.jpg 2161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n<figcaption>Part of the final design implementation.</figcaption>\n<hr>\n<p><em>Up to now (27.02.2021), the website is still under construction and has not been released yet.</em></p>","frontmatter":{"layout":"post","title":"MATRIX Robotics Website","path":"/matrix-robotics/","category":["UX","UI","Frontend"],"skill":null,"role":["UI (Figma)","Front-end Development (HTML, SASS)","Branding (design system)"],"description":"UI design system for MATRIX Robotics' enterprise website in compliance with its branding style and the technical requirements based on WordPress","date":"2021","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":500,"height":375,"src":"/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/0f3a1/cover.jpg","srcSet":"/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/0f3a1/cover.jpg 1x,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/f9913/cover.jpg 1.5x,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/a7715/cover.jpg 2x","srcWebp":"/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/e9589/cover.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/e9589/cover.webp 1x,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/e557c/cover.webp 1.5x,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/e30b5/cover.webp 2x"},"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3333333333333333,"src":"/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/a1eb1/cover.jpg","srcSet":"/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/4fa6c/cover.jpg 200w,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/64b17/cover.jpg 400w,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/a1eb1/cover.jpg 800w,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/a6c62/cover.jpg 1200w,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/70ff9/cover.jpg 1600w,\n/static/8f423627dd709d77b6f960c3988e2ef0/f0a07/cover.jpg 2400w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}